  "Description": {
    "English": "An exclusive <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Freighter Engine Flare Modifier</span>.<br><br>Organically altering the hue of freighter exhaust, this engine modification utilizes the bioluminescence of abyssal sea creatures to generate its striking turquoise coloration.<br><br>Transform the appearance of your freighter at the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Upgrade Control Terminal</span> on the <VAL_ON>bridge<>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "专属<span class=\"name name-stellar\">货船驱动信号器修改器</span>。<br><br>这种驱动器改装利用深渊海洋生物的生物发光有机地改变了货船排气的色调，生成了引人注目的绿松石色。<br><br>在<VAL_ON>舰桥<>上的<span class=\"name name-technology\">升级控制终端</span>改变货船外观。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "特殊的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">貨船引擎火光改造器</span>。<br><br>以有機的方法改變貨船廢氣顏色，這個引擎改造利用深海生物的生物光，產生其引人注目的綠松色。<br><br>可在<VAL_ON>艦橋<>上的<span class=\"name name-technology\">升級控制終端站</span>裡變更你的貨船外觀。"
  },
